Francis Odega bụ onye na-eme ejije na-atọ ọchị nke Naijiria nke a maara nke ọma maka ihe nkiri vidio na-atọ ọchị nke ya nke gbasara ma kesaa n'Ịntanet. O mere ka ọ pụta ìhè ka ọ na-enweta nkwekọrịta nkwado na nkwanye ùgwù site n'aka ndị ama ama na mba ọzọ, ihe atụ bụ 50 cent, onye Odega kwuru na ọ gbasoro ya na Instagram
Francis nwetara nzere bachelọ na Economics mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Ambrose Alli

Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị mbụ na-eme ihe ọchị nke Night Of A Thousand Laughs comedy show. N'afọ 2013, Francis nwetara ihe nrite "Best Actor" ya na Hlomla Dandala na "Best African Collaboration" na 2013 Ghana Movie Awards. Francis bịara bụrụ onye a ma ama mgbe ihe nkiri sitere na usoro ihe nkiri Back From South Africa kụrụ ịntanetị na ndị ama ama dị ka 50 Cent na Tinie Tempah na-ekerịta vidiyo vidiyo nke ihe nkiri ahụ na Instagram
Ihe nkiri ahụ na-egosi ya na-ekwu okwu n'ụzọ na-atọ ọchị n'olu Amerịka.
Mgbe eji vidio ahụ gbasasịrị, Francis bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta nkwado na ụlọ ọrụ nkwukọrịta Etisalat dị ka onye nnọchi anya ya.
